Class Adapter.JsonArrayCallback

    public abstract static class Adapter.JsonArrayCallback
extends Adapter.JsonCallback
    A callback that returns a JSON array. If the return value is not a JSON array or "null", then the Adapter.Callback.onError(Throwable) method is called.
